code: import axios from'axios';var userRegion=localStorage.getItem('userRegion');if(userRegion){userRegion=userRegion.replace(/ /g,"_");}var FETCH_PLAYER="/api/v1/players/search?username=";var FETCH_TOP_PLAYERS="/api/v1/players/top?region=";var FETCH_LATEST_PLAYERS="/api/v1/players/latest?region=";var searchPlayer=function searchPlayer(username){return axios.get(FETCH_PLAYER+username+'&region='+userRegion).then(function(response){return response.data.nickname;}).catch(function(error){});};var fetchTopPlayer=function fetchTopPlayer(){return axios.get(FETCH_TOP_PLAYERS+userRegion).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(error){console.log(error);});};var fetchLatestPlayers=function fetchLatestPlayers(){return axios.get(FETCH_LATEST_PLAYERS+userRegion).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(error){console.log(error);});};export default{searchPlayer:searchPlayer,fetchTopPlayer:fetchTopPlayer,fetchLatestPlayers:fetchLatestPlayers};
